[49m[38;5;10m+    191[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## General Architecture Pattern
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    192[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    193[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A healthcare care-coordination assistant decomposes into ten logical stages: enrollment with multi-stakeholder consent, longitudinal-store initialization with care-plan integration, channel entry with disclosure, input safety screening with continuous emergency screening, identity-and-context loading with multi-source integration, conversation handling with commitment-tracking-aware orchestration, output safety screening with consent-scope verification, escalation routing with care-team-workflow integration, write-back to clinical systems where consent permits, and audit logging with appropriate retention discipline. The cross-cutting concerns from recipes 11.1 through 11.8 carry forward; this recipe adds five new ones (multi-source information integration as architectural primitive, commitment-tracking with structured state across episodes, multi-stakeholder consent-scope enforcement, care-gap-definition library governance, and write-back to clinical systems with named-recipient routing).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    194[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    195[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    196[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ENROLLMENT + CONSENT ──────────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    197[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    198[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient enrolls via institution app, by referral from  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    199[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    care team, or by population-health-driven outreach]    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    200[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Eligibility check (medical complexity criteria,      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    201[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      institutional policy on bot-supported populations,   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    202[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      exclusion criteria)                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    203[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Documented consent specific to multi-source data     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    204[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      integration (because the bot fetches across multiple │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    205[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      clinical systems, the consent scope is broader than  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    206[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      single-clinician)                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    207[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Family-caregiver authorization with named caregiver, │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    208[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      granular scope, revocability                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    209[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot-initiated proactive engagement opt-in            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Crisis-resource information surfaced                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Privacy posture explained in plain language          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team-sharing consent collected separately       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: signed consent record; enrollment confirmation;│
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    initialization of longitudinal store]                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── LONGITUDINAL STORE INIT WITH CARE-PLAN INTEGRATION ┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient-bot longitudinal store with multi-source picture] │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active conditions on the problem list                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    224[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Current medications (reconciled across sources)         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    225[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Allergies                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    226[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care team membership (PCP, specialists, care manager,   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      pharmacist, others)                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    228[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent encounters (last 12-24 months)                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    229[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Upcoming appointments                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    230[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Open referrals (with lifecycle status)                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Open orders (lab, imaging, DME, home health)            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Open prior-authorization requests                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care plan (CarePlan resource where present, or          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      assembled from after-visit summaries and discharge      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      instructions)                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care goals (Goal resource where present)                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient-stated preferences (preferred name, language,   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      pronouns, channel preferences, family-caregiver         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      consent scope, communication preferences)               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient-stated history (preserved separately from       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      authoritative clinical record, marked as patient-       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      reported)                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Family-caregiver authorizations                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation history (initially empty)                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent care-gap status                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent transition-of-care episodes (with cadence state) │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent escalation history                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Storage architecture]                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Structured data: DynamoDB tables                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation transcript: S3 with vector retrieval       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent-context summary: cached, refreshed on            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      conversation                                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Source-of-truth pointers preserved (for clinical-data,  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      the EHR or the upstream source remains authoritative;   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      the bot's longitudinal store is a coordination          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      augment)                                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: longitudinal store ready for coordination         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    conversations, with multi-source integration active]     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    265[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── CHANNEL ENTRY WITH DISCLOSURE ─────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient-initiated entry]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - In-app chat (most common)                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - SMS (where supported, with consent)                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Web chat                                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Voice channel (where supported)                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    272[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Family-caregiver-initiated entry where authorized    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    273[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    274[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Bot-initiated entry, calibrated to care episode]       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    275[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Post-discharge cadence (day 3, day 7, day 14, day 30 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    276[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      after a hospitalization, with cadence calibrated to  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    277[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      the discharge diagnosis and risk profile)            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    278[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pre-procedure check-in (typically seventy-two hours  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    279[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      before)                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    280[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Post-referral-order check-in (typically five business│
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    281[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      days after a referral is ordered if no scheduling    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    282[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      activity has occurred)                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    283[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Post-order check-in for labs, imaging, DME, home     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    284[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      health if no completion within expected window       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    285[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-gap-closure check-in for overdue gaps           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    286[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team-requested check-in                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    287[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot-initiation respects patient quiet hours, channel │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    288[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      preferences, and engagement intensity preference     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    289[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    290[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Disclosure refresh per session or per defined cadence] │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    291[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "I'm a chat tool, not a person"                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    292[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "I'm here to help with coordination, not to give     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    293[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      medical advice or change your treatment plan"        │
