[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    298[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient acknowledges or continues                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    299[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    300[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Conversation session bootstrap]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    301[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Generate session_id                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    302[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Capture channel, authentication context, requesting  │
