[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    355[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Upcoming-appointments retrieval                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    356[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent after-visit-summaries retrieval               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    357[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Discharge-instructions retrieval (where applicable)  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    358[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-gap-status retrieval                            │
