[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    415[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - emergency_route                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    416[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - fhir_communication_write (consent-gated)           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    417[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - fhir_task_write (consent-gated)                    │
