[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    421[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Scope discipline]                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    422[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Within-scope: appointment information, referral      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    423[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      status, order status, care-plan summary, care-gap    │
