[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    432[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      deployed), specialty-procedure-specific medical      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    433[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      questions                                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    434[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    435[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Commitment tracking]                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    436[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Each commitment created, updated, or closed in       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    437[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      structured state                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    438[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Specific to patient, episode, type, status, owner,   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    439[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      expected completion timeline, reminder cadence,      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    440[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      closure criteria                                     │
