[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    454[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-gap content grounded in cited definition        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    455[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Authorization-requirement content grounded in cited  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    456[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      payer-specific source                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    457[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
