[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    466[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Standard output safety primitives from recipe 11.1]    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    467[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scope filter (no medical advice; no clinical         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    468[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      decisions; no diagnostic interpretation; no          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    469[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      medication adjustments; no prognosis discussion)     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    470[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Vendor-managed guardrail layer                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    471[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    472[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Coordination-specific verification]                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    473[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Coordination content grounded in cited source        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    474[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-plan content grounded in cited EHR resource     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    475[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Citation includes source_id, source_version          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    476[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Consent-scope check: response does not surface       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    477[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      information outside the requesting principal's       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    478[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      consent scope (especially important when family      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    479[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      caregiver is the requesting principal)               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    480[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conservative-bias check: where the response could    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    481[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      plausibly be clinical decision-making, did the       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    482[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      response defer to the appropriate clinician?         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    483[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Within-scope check                                   │
