[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    486[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Loop-closing-honor check: if a commitment was        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    487[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      tracked, did the response surface or honor it        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    488[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      appropriately?                                       │
