[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    499[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Escalation triggers]                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    500[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient explicitly requests human                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    501[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Out-of-scope clinical question                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    502[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Sensitive disclosure pattern                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    503[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot confidence below threshold                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    504[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Source-reconciliation inconsistency that is          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    505[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      clinically significant                               │
