[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    507[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      barrier (patient cannot afford the lab; patient      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    508[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      cannot transport to the appointment)                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    509[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Worsening trajectory in patient-reported symptoms    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    510[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Loop-closing failure (referral not scheduled despite │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    511[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      multiple reminders)                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    512[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Family-caregiver concern requiring care-manager      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    513[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      attention                                            │
