[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    625[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Outcome correlation as long-time-horizon commitment]   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    626[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Multi-quarter to multi-year                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    627[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Owned jointly by quality leadership, operations,     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    628[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      and data science                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    629[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-condition, per-cohort tracking                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    630[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Outcome metrics include readmission rates, care-gap  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    631[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      closure rates, missed-appointment rates, medication- │
